(1, 'Hisense 32-Inch Class H4 Series LED Roku Smart TV with Alexa Compatibility (32H4F, 2020 Model)', 'Combining rich 720p picture quality, intuitively smart Roku TV platform, built-in Wi-Fi, and innovative technologies, Hisense H4F series smart TVs are great for all your needs&mdash;streaming, cable, satellite, gaming, and free over-the-air TV.\r\nEnjoy all the key moments in fast-paced sports, movies, and games with motion rate 120-image processing, minimizing picture lag to create a crystal clear image without motion blur.\r\nRoku TV&#039;s simplified home screen and streamlined remote provide easy to access your cable box or HDTV antenna, one-touch access to favorite channels and streaming services, and access to over 5,000 streaming channels and 500,000 movies and TV episodes.\r\nControl the TV with your iOS or android device via the easy-to-use Roku TV remote app, or use your voice to power your TV on and off, change channels, search for shows, and more through an Alexa-enabled device or google assistant (both sold separately).\r\nThe vesa measurements for this TV are 200 x 200mm, for wall mounting purposes. Wall mount sold separately.\r\nMeasuring 28.9 by 17 by 2.8 inches (28.9 by 18.7 by 6.7 inches with included stand, LxWxH), the 32H4F is backed by a one-year manufacturer&#039;s warranty, and includes a Roku remote (batteries included), power cable, and quick start guide.\r\nPower source type: corded electric', '119.99', NULL, 'images/5f9e2233d9833526525a9d5d455dca3df025e919679e0901099d1b6803c92ed545c6680b7e511b06fb2bb104cc1ec3269dd995a833b1ce3785cc5fd1646c4d1b.jpg', 'hisense-32-inch-class-h4-series-led-roku-smart-tv-with-alexa-compatibility-32h4f-2020-model', 50, 1, 4, '2020-09-14 09:06:09', '2020-09-14 09:06:09', 20),
(2, 'Hisense 40-Inch 40H5500F Class H55 Series Android Smart TV with Voice Remote (2020 Model)', 'Inputs &amp; Outputs: 2 HDMI ports, 1 Ethernet port, 2 USB Ports (v 2.0), 1 Digital Audio Output (Optical), 1 RCA Composite Video Input, 1 L/R Audio Input for composite\r\nMeasuring 35.6 x 20.4 x 3.2 inches and 12.8 pounds (35.6 x 22.4 x 8 inches with included stand, LxWxH and 13 pounds), the 40h5500f has a 1-year manufacturer&#039;s warranty, and includes a remote (batteries included), power cable, and quick start guide.\r\nEnjoy crisp, immersive audio from the two 7-watt speakers and DTS studio sound virtual surround sound, or wirelessly connect a compatible sound bar, headphone, or stereo components using built-in Bluetooth connectivity.\r\nEnjoy all the key moments in fast-paced sports, movies, and games with motion rate 120-image processing, minimizing picture lag to create a clear image without motion blur.\r\nThe vesa measurements for this TV are 100 x 200mm / m6, for wall mounting purposes. Wall mount sold separately.\r\nCombining rich 1080p picture quality, the voice-enabled android TV platform, built-in Wi-Fi, and innovative technologies, Hisense h55 series smart TVs are great for all your needs &mdash; streaming, cable, satellite, gaming, and free over-the-air TV.\r\nControl the TV via the easy-to-use voice-enabled remote &mdash; open or search for apps, control the volume and inputs, or search for your favorite TV shows and movies.', '189.99', '160.99', 'images/5220104fb3e43b308edcfa99eb604241202612a64adb28c776ee11291fb83521a869bae07836cf050c7de707170fafdd08df2886ad68198e398315530247b32e.jpg', 'hisense-40-inch-40h5500f-class-h55-series-android-smart-tv-with-voice-remote-2020-model', 20, 1, 4, '2020-09-14 09:16:54', '2020-09-14 09:16:54', 20),
